Title : Template:Dormant/doc
Text : {{Documentation subpage}}
To mark a proposed policy (or other community document) as dormant, add the following above its lead:

{{tlx|Dormant}}

Do not substitute this template.

The {{para|category}} parameter can be used to override the auto-categorisation feature of this template. Otherwise, the use of this template will categorise the target page into [[:Category:Wikipedia archives]]. Use {{para|category|Category:Vegetables}} to categorise the page into [[:Category:Vegetables]] instead of the usual category, or use {{para|category}} (nothing typed after <code>=</code>) to do no categorisation through the template.


In addition, a shortcut can be added to this template by using the following syntax:

{{Tlx|Dormant|SHORTCUT}}

Up to 5 shortcuts can be added to this template in this fashion:

{{Tlx|Dormant|SHORTCUT1|SHORTCUT2|SHORTCUT3|SHORTCUT4|SHORTCUT5}}

<includeonly>{{#ifeq:{{SUBPAGENAME}}|sandbox||
<!-- Template categories  -->
[[Category:Wikipedia archives]]
[[Category:Wikipedia header templates]]

}}</includeonly>
